# Project Context

- Monorepo: `core/`, `instagram-bot/`, `electron-app/`, `admin/`
- Playwright bot in `@buzzbo/instagram-bot`; shared types/API in `@buzzbo/core`
- **Electron-only client** — run via `npm run dev:electron` (no CLI); backend via `npm run dev`
- Admin API URL: `BUZZBO_ADMIN_API_URL` (fallback `ADMIN_API_URL`)
- Educational use only — automating Instagram violates ToS; account ban risk
- Match existing patterns: class-based modules, chalk `Logger`, async/await
